Step Challenge: Teams compete to log the most steps over a week or month.
Healthy Habit Streak: Teams work to maintain a streak of healthy behaviors (like drinking enough water, exercising, or eating fruits and veggies) for a set period.
Fitness Class Participation: Teams earn points based on attendance in fitness classes or group workouts.
Weekend Warrior Challenge: Encourage outdoor activities during weekends, with teams competing for the most collective hours spent on physical activities.
Daily Activity Goals: Set daily activity goals, with teams competing to meet or exceed them consistently.
Weekly Fitness Bingo: Create a bingo card with various fitness and wellness activities; teams earn points by completing rows or the entire card.
Check-In System: Users can check in for team activities or events, with points awarded for participation.
